<!DOCTYPE html>

<html class="light" lang="vi"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&amp;family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<script id="tailwind-config">
      tailwind.config = {
        darkMode: "class",
        theme: {
          extend: {
            "colors": {
                    "on-secondary-fixed-variant": "#375c75",
                    "inverse-on-surface": "#9c9d9d",
                    "outline-variant": "#acadad",
                    "primary-container": "#fd8603",
                    "on-tertiary-fixed-variant": "#644e00",
                    "background": "#f6f6f6",
                    "on-tertiary-fixed": "#423200",
                    "surface-container-lowest": "#ffffff",
                    "surface-container-highest": "#dbdddd",
                    "on-primary-fixed-variant": "#4f2600",
                    "surface-container-high": "#e1e3e3",
                    "surface-dim": "#d2d5d5",
                    "tertiary": "#715800",
                    "error": "#b02500",
                    "on-secondary": "#e9f4ff",
                    "on-tertiary": "#fff1d6",
                    "on-secondary-container": "#2d526b",
                    "tertiary-fixed-dim": "#edbe23",
                    "surface-container": "#e7e8e8",
                    "surface-tint": "#8e4900",
                    "secondary-dim": "#2e536c",
                    "on-error": "#ffefec",
                    "surface-container-low": "#f0f1f1",
                    "on-tertiary-container": "#594500",
                    "secondary-fixed": "#bce1ff",
                    "error-container": "#f95630",
                    "inverse-surface": "#0c0f0f",
                    "surface-variant": "#dbdddd",
                    "on-secondary-fixed": "#183f57",
                    "on-background": "#2d2f2f",
                    "surface": "#f6f6f6",
                    "primary-dim": "#7d3f00",
                    "on-surface": "#2d2f2f",
                    "on-primary-fixed": "#0f0400",
                    "tertiary-container": "#fccc33",
                    "on-error-container": "#520c00",
                    "outline": "#757777",
                    "secondary-fixed-dim": "#aed3f1",
                    "tertiary-dim": "#634d00",
                    "on-primary": "#fff0e7",
                    "inverse-primary": "#fd8603",
                    "error-dim": "#b92902",
                    "primary": "#8e4900",
                    "secondary": "#3b5f78",
                    "primary-fixed": "#fd8603",
                    "on-primary-container": "#421e00",
                    "primary-fixed-dim": "#e97b00",
                    "tertiary-fixed": "#fccc33",
                    "secondary-container": "#bce1ff",
                    "surface-bright": "#f6f6f6",
                    "on-surface-variant": "#5a5c5c"
            },
            "borderRadius": {
                    "DEFAULT": "0.25rem",
                    "lg": "0.5rem",
                    "xl": "0.75rem",
                    "full": "9999px"
            },
            "fontFamily": {
                    "headline": ["Plus Jakarta Sans"],
                    "body": ["Inter"],
                    "label": ["Inter"]
            }
          },
        },
      }
    </script>
<style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f6f6f6; }
        .font-headline { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
        .material-symbols-outlined { font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24; }
        .glass-nav { backdrop-filter: blur(20px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px); }
        .hero-gradient { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e4900 0%, #fd8603 100%); }
        .no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-on-background">
<!-- TopNavBar -->
<nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-900/80 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center px-6 py-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="text-2xl font-black italic tracking-tighter text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-500 font-headline">Linhfood</div>
<div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
<a class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-orange-500 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] font-bold text-sm tracking-tight cursor-pointer active:scale-95" href="#">Trang chủ</a>
<a class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 font-extrabold border-b-2 border-orange-600 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-sm tracking-tight cursor-pointer active:scale-95" href="#">Menu</a>
<a class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-orange-500 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] font-bold text-sm tracking-tight cursor-pointer active:scale-95" href="#">Combo</a>
<a class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-orange-500 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] font-bold text-sm tracking-tight cursor-pointer active:scale-95" href="#">Khuyến mãi</a>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<button class="relative p-2 text-gray-700 hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="shopping_cart">shopping_cart</span>
<span class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container text-[10px] font-bold px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">3</span>
</button>
<button class="bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container px-5 py-2 rounded-lg font-headline font-bold text-sm hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all">Giỏ hàng</button>
</div>
</div>
</nav>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto pt-24 pb-12 px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
<!-- SideNavBar -->
<aside class="w-full md:w-64 flex-shrink-0">
<div class="sticky top-24 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-950 rounded-xl p-4 border-r border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800">
<div class="mb-6 px-2">
<h2 class="text-orange-600 font-bold font-headline text-lg">Danh mục</h2>
<p class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-body">Linhfood Menu</p>
</div>
<nav class="flex flex-col gap-2">
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 py-3 px-4 rounded-lg bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 border-r-4 border-orange-600 transition-all duration-200 hover:translate-x-1 font-headline font-semibold text-sm cursor-pointer" href="#an-vat">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl" data-icon="fastfood">fastfood</span>
<span>Ăn vặt</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 py-3 px-4 rounded-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all duration-200 hover:translate-x-1 font-headline font-semibold text-sm cursor-pointer" href="#do-uong">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl" data-icon="local_bar">local_bar</span>
<span>Đồ uống</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 py-3 px-4 rounded-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all duration-200 hover:translate-x-1 font-headline font-semibold text-sm cursor-pointer" href="#combo">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl" data-icon="layers">layers</span>
<span>Combo</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 py-3 px-4 rounded-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all duration-200 hover:translate-x-1 font-headline font-semibold text-sm cursor-pointer" href="#do-an-chinh">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl" data-icon="restaurant">restaurant</span>
<span>Đồ ăn chính</span>
</a>
</nav>
</div>
</aside>
<!-- Main Content -->
<main class="flex-1 space-y-16">
<!-- Hero Promo Banner (Asymmetric Layout) -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl hero-gradient p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
<div class="z-10 text-white max-w-md">
<span class="bg-tertiary-container text-on-tertiary-container text-xs font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 inline-block">Flash Deal</span>
<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-headline leading-tight mb-4">Combo Bùng Nổ Vị Giác!</h1>
<p class="text-white/80 mb-8 font-body">Tiết kiệm đến 30% khi đặt các bộ combo ăn vặt và đồ uống đặc biệt chỉ có tại Linhfood.</p>
<button class="bg-white text-primary font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all font-headline">Khám phá ngay</button>
</div>
<div class="relative w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 flex-shrink-0">
<img alt="Delicious Burger Combo" class="w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-2xl rotate-6 transform hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500" data-alt="overhead shot of a gourmet beef burger with melting cheese, crispy fries, and a refreshing soda on a vibrant orange background" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDjocqwNnHD7IVA-PUL9sDDxSoiGSQfkB_xwtmC0EqSQts1vlBxRB2CSp-ZQtmvv6Mlh38jW3zTAFDcrZmQKxdqbhYc8jQe3jB4Y2b3CPLkWSBBSDsMpi9Kn6932z5xOdcObdpH4Ka15aJvwq-c074SZauAFrWKKo7NWPCl0Ia4AwsgOakgHTaog7QRi3AzAU5M31DeQ19d75jyQvhDUCbfOQ_8yvJNojRUz-OeVUTVQovTEQKRAoZ2tKGtmVongTgN_srLoFlYOCI"/>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Category: Ăn vặt -->
<section class="scroll-mt-28" id="an-vat">
<div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-8">
<div>
<h2 class="text-3xl font-black font-headline text-on-background tracking-tight">Ăn vặt</h2>
<div class="h-1.5 w-12 bg-primary-container mt-2 rounded-full"></div>
</div>
<a class="text-primary font-bold text-sm flex items-center gap-1 hover:gap-2 transition-all" href="#">Xem tất cả <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span></a>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<!-- Product Card 1 -->
<div class="group bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.03] hover:shadow-[0_40px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] relative">
